{"tid":1114294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【元朗反黑】卧底破賭檔毒窟骨場拘413人　17歲酒客無牌酒吧被捕","createTime":"2019-04-18T11:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T11:22:23.000Z","uid":246371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4dc0869e96d70097ce8436c07d29a0c13e846a6f","tid":1114294,"uid":246371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T11:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ML6rVmX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FML6rVmX.png&h=3be81365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NhdJXAo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNhdJXAo.png&h=83a36277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗警區總督察（刑事）吳家麒總督察表示，警方在去年底發現區內有一團夥經營不同類型的非法活動，包括非法賭檔、街頭賭檔、利用足浴店掩飾的色情場所等，為保障其業務，不法分子甚至會預備武器作械鬥之用及偷車，嚴重影響區內民生。有見及此，警方在本年2月開始主動打擊不法活動，派出兩名探員喬裝顧客，深入這些非法活動場所收集情報及證據。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vx6O8Ha.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvx6O8Ha.png&h=66f256e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYgGKfw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYgGKfw.png&h=b1597a02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PaM0fnb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPaM0fnb.png&h=807d0045&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5UTU4fx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5UTU4fx.png&h=14b35221&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHsChAy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHsChAy.png&h=fd1b9d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當掌握相關情報及證據後，警方發現有持牌遊戲機中心利用釣魚機等遊戲，透過與顧客兌分派發彩金，從中抽佣，不法分子更會向顧客提議前往其他不法場所娛樂，包括樓上釣魚機檔或麻雀檔等。經深入調查後，警方鎖定該三合會團夥的骨幹成員，以及他們所有在區內的非法場所地點。本月12日傍晚起，元朗警區突擊搜查區內35個地點，其間更搗破位於公屋的武器庫及作毒品銷售中心單位。吳家麒指，行動共拘捕逾400人，其中25人屬於團夥的骨幹成員。該團夥利用不同類型的非法活動帶來可觀收入，相信是次行動已成功瓦解該團夥，打擊他們的非法活動及非法收入。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pawzjOY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpawzjOY.png&h=d0f1ded6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1efa9323704fb4c45180154a2930a1757b2f321b","tid":1114294,"uid":246371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T11:20:56.000Z","msg":"一個行動就拉咗400幾個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383a57f2be72e96c8cdd237ee9875ed64c667b25","tid":1114294,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1efa9323704fb4c45180154a2930a1757b2f321b","tid":1114294,"uid":246371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T11:20:56.000Z","msg":"一個行動就拉咗400幾個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"30幾個地點 都唔算多啦"}]}